content.rendered:
Directed by Kabir Khan.

Written by Parveez Sheikh. Manu Rishi Chadha.

Cast Salman Khan(Laxman). Sohail Khan(Bharat). Om Puri(Banne Chacha). Mohd. Zeeshan Ayyub(Narayan). Yashpal Sharma(Major Rajbir Tokas). Zhu Zhu(Liling). Matin Rey Tangu(Guo). Brijendra Kala(Shoe Shopkeeper). Isha Talwar(Maya). Jason D’Souza(Little Laxman (6) (as Jason DSouza)). Matt Kramer(Father Fredrick). Neeraj Khetrapal(Laxmans Teacher (as Neeraj Khetarpal)). Kapil Sharma(Laxmans Father). Mitansh Lulla(Little Laxman (12) (as Mitansh S Lulla)). Ricky Patel(Little Bharat (6)). Abhikalp Gagdekar(Little Narayan). Kamlesh Shah(Gandhiji). Vivek Pandey(Narayans Sidekick 1). Amarnath Verma(Narayans Sidekick 2). Navdeep Tomar(Jco). Karan Maan(Commanding Officer (as Karan Maan)). Amit Singh(Pan Singh). Kishan Juggler(Fire Breather). Varun Kulkarni(Show Announcer). Jahaan Yadav(Indian Soldier 2). Alok Gagdekar(Phone Man). Sunil Uppal(Dhaba Owner). Narendra Khatri(Dhaba Waiter). Kumud Johry(Laxmans Neighbour). Mandeep Singh Rathour(Indian Soldier 3 (as Mandeep Singh)). Chien Ho Liao(Chinese Soldier 1). Thomas Chen(Chinese Soldier 2). Thutan Gombu(Chinese Soldier 3). Sooraj Shetty(Chinese Soldier 4). Rakesh Thakur(Chinese Soldier 5). Champ Thapa(Chinese Soldier 6). Akash(Chinese Soldier 7). 

Languages Hindi. English.

Producers Amar Butala. Rajan Kapoor. Rajan Kapoor. Salman Khan. Garima Mehta.

Production Kabir Khan Film. Salman Khan Film.
